title: Beavis and Butt-Head collection by Woo
description:
Beavis and Butt-Head collection by Woo

 197 episodes WITHOUT music videos.

 This collection scavenged from other collections over the net.
 All music videos are cut out, formats are DivX & XviD,
 quality varies from good to average (few are bad).

 Some episodes aspect ratios must be set override to 4:3
 (In Media Player Classic - View/Video Frame/Override Aspect Ratio/4:3 + Keep Aspect Ratio)
 (In BS Player - Video/Aspect Ratio/4:3)


 s03e27 - A Very Special Christmas With Beavis and Butt-head (17 Dec 1993)
   and
 \&#039;Beavis and Butt-head Do America\&#039; movie (20 Dec 1996) (s06e08)
  - are not here.
